---
title: Creamy Squash Linguine with Goat Cheese, Almonds and Crispy Shallots
description: Squash, leeks and creamy goat cheese melt into a silky sauce for quick-cooking fresh linguine! Top it all off with a crispy, crunchy topping of toasted almonds, crispy shallots, Parmesan, rosemary and lemon zest, and you'll be scraping up every last bite.

